                <a href="topic.asp?ARCHIVE=true&TOPIC_ID=21614"><img src="images/icon_go_left.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="Previous Topic: Burning Affliction items?" title="Previous Topic: Burning Affliction items?" align="top" hspace="6" /></a><b><font face="arial" size="2" color="#000000"> Topic </font></b><a href="topic.asp?ARCHIVE=true&TOPIC_ID=21610"><img src="images/icon_go_right.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="Next Topic: one difficult question for the VT/EP raiding Necro" title="Next Topic: one difficult question for the VT/EP raiding Necro" align="top" hspace="6" /></a></font></b></td>
